Package: ooim2mr
Type: Package
Title: Functions For Gathering Science Data From The OOI M2M System Via R
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Ian Black
Maintainer: Ocean Observatories Initiative <help@oceanobservatories.org>
Description: This package provides a set of functions that allows users to access and 
    download OOI scientific data through requests to the OOI machine-to-machine system.
    Use of this package requires preliminary knowledge of OOI assets and their locations.
    A list of OOI sites can be found here: https://oceanobservatories.org/site-list/
Depends: R(>= 3.6.3)
Imports: httr,
         jsonlite,
         ncdf4,
         rio,
         stringr
Suggests: 
    ggplot2,
    RColorBrewer,
License: CC0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
URL: https://github.com/IanTBlack/ooim2mr
BugReports: https://github.com/IanTBlack/ooim2mr/issues
